# ==============================================================================
# IMPORTANT: Files That SHOULD Be Tracked
# ==============================================================================
# The following files are intentionally NOT ignored and should remain in git:
#
# Model Files (external dependencies - not owned by this project)
# These files come from external repositories and should be downloaded via setup scripts
# They are not part of our intellectual property
kokoro.onnx                        # Main TTS model file (310MB)
kokoro-v1_0.pth                   # Voice model file (312MB)
kokoro-v1.0.int8.onnx             # Quantized model (88MB)
voices-v1.0.bin                    # Voice data file
*.onnx                            # ONNX model files (external)
*.pth                             # PyTorch model files (external)
*.bin                             # Binary model files (external)
#
# Core Configuration:
# - requirements*.txt              # Python dependencies
# - pyproject.toml                # Project configuration
# - Makefile                      # Build and deployment scripts
# - Dockerfile*                   # Container definitions
# - docker-compose*.yml           # Docker orchestration
# - README.md                     # Project documentation
#
# Scripts and Tools:
# - scripts/                      # Benchmark and utility scripts
# - docs/                         # Documentation (keep source, ignore builds)
# - api/                          # Main application code
# - dashboard/                    # Frontend code (keep source, ignore dist)
# - raycast/                      # Raycast integration (keep source, ignore dist)
#
# ==============================================================================
# Maintenance Notes
# ==============================================================================
# To check what files would be ignored:
#   git status --ignored
#
# To see what would be added if patterns were removed:
#   git add . && git status
#
# To clean untracked files that should be ignored:
#   git clean -fdx
